title: Shameless Grounds
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Fast food, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Saint Louis coffee cafe with a large food menu. Vegan and vegetarian items labeled and includes soup, salads, sandwiches, eggplant and mushroom skewers, Asian slaw, and hummus. Free Wi-Fi and a lending library with a variety of media related to human sexuality, entertainment, and education. Previously at 2650 Sidney St.
